   - Proposed date
   - Fee offered (if any)
   - Their message
4. **Set Status:** ğŸ“© New Inquiry (you can update this later)
5. **Click "ğŸ’¾ SAVE"**

### Updating Speaking Engagement Status
1. **Click on the engagement from the list**
2. **Update the Status as things progress:**
   - ğŸ“© New Inquiry
   - ğŸ“ Initial Contact Made
   - ğŸ’¬ In Discussion
   - ğŸ“… Scheduled
